description: Jazz Education non-profit Jazz House Kids hosted Pat Metheny for a High School masterclass on June 10th 2008. Over 100 high school jazz students from New Jersey spent 2 hours with Metheny. This years masterclass will feature Chris Botti on May 6th. www.jazzhousekids.org
